::DeathStorm/Shredder::

DeathStorm growls as Sinesis' shot hits him in the back. He jumps 
backwards over Sinesis. One predacon he could handle, but two could 
be trouble. He turns around, transforms into beast mode, and flies 
off.

"Computer, cloak." He says into his ship's portable controlls. 
Several miles away, his ship cloaks itself as he flies off toward the 
alliance base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder stands up. "Thanks." He says drily to Sinesis.
